<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>WebQuant</title><link href="http://webquant.ru/" rel="alternate"></link><link href="your_site_domain/feeds/linux.atom.xml" rel="self"></link><id>http://webquant.ru/</id><updated>2014-11-08T13:37:00+03:00</updated><entry><title>Настраиваем Ubuntu после запуска.</title><link href="http://webquant.ru/posts/ubuntu" rel="alternate"></link><updated>2014-11-08T13:37:00+03:00</updated><author><name>admin</name></author><id>tag:webquant.ru,2014-11-08:posts/ubuntu</id><summary type="html">&lt;h3&gt;Google Drive&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;add&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;repository&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;ppa&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;thefanclub&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;grive&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;tools&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;update&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;install&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;grive&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;tools&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="cp"&gt;#в поиске набираем Grive setup и следуем инструкциям&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h3&gt;Отключаем комерческий сервис в меню Dash&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;gsettings&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;set&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;canonical&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Unity&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;Lenses&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;disabled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;scopes&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s"&gt;&amp;quot;[&amp;#39;more_suggestions-amazon.scope&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;more_suggestions-u1ms.scope&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;more_suggestions-populartracks.scope&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;music-musicstore.scope&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;more_suggestions-ebay.scope&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;more_suggestions-ubuntushop.scope&amp;#39;, &amp;#39;more_suggestions-skimlinks.scope&amp;#39;]&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h3&gt;Добавляем ключ от репозитория&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;adv&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;keyserver&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;keyserver&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;ubuntu&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;com&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;recv&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;keys&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;FC91AE7E&lt;/span&gt; 
&lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;list&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h3&gt;Разблокировать dpkg&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Часто появляется ошибка: &lt;em&gt;Unable to lock the administration directory (/var/lib/dpkg/) is another process using it&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;ps&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;A&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;grep&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;kill&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;9&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;process&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;id&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;kill&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;9&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;2345&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;h3&gt;Создание загрузочной флешки из образа диска&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;dd&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="k"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;home&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;username&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;path&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;filename&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;iso&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;of&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;dev&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;/&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;sdb&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;bs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="mi"&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;M&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ставить на форматированную fat32 флешку.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;включить галку - загрузочный диск.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ставлю на sdb раздел, на sdb1 не получается.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;bs=16m сколько за раз записывается.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Как удалить приложение со всеми зависимостями&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;sudo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;apt&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;remove&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;firefox&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;*&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;#&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;звездочку&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="err"&gt;добавляем&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</summary><category term="linux"></category></entry><entry><title>Базовые команды Linux.</title><link href="http://webquant.ru/posts/linux-base" rel="alternate"></link><updated>2014-11-01T22:27:00+03:00</updated><author><name>admin</name></author><id>tag:webquant.ru,2014-11-01:posts/linux-base</id><summary type="html">&lt;h3&gt;Основные команды&lt;/h3&gt;
